    "name": "A Rat's Life: The Cat Conspiracy",
    "steam_appid": 1790350,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/5ea8052d29e2ec94d2be51f542b78738.avif?t=1728683039\" width=612 height=429 /></span>A Rat’s Life: The Cat Conspiracy is a story-rich action-adventure game that blends Collect-a-Thon and Metroidvania mechanics. It aims to recapture the exciting vibe of classic Rareware games on Nintendo 64, such as Banjo-Kazooie and Conker’s Bad Fur Day,  and features deep lore and adult humor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/c18809c845b931c759d30ecb278dfedf.webp?t=1728683039\" width=614 height=45 /></span>The game is set within a microsociety that feels vibrant and alive, thanks to a rich story, memorable characters, a fair amount of comedy and events based on a day cycle system. The most dedicated players will have the opportunity to delve intensely into the detailed story, while others may choose to stick to the essentials</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/f4025a648f48d77b19ddff775c62d183.poster.avif?t=1728683039\" width=614 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/f4025a648f48d77b19ddff775c62d183.webm?t=1728683039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/f4025a648f48d77b19ddff775c62d183.mp4?t=1728683039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/8753313d59d6cd16e06f40ffd084a2ce.webp?t=1728683039\" width=614 height=45 /></span>Progress through a sprawling abandoned zoo, forming an interconnected world with diverse environments, as you learn and upgrade a wide range of abilities. The Metroidvania mechanics are also narrative-based, insofar as gaining favor from specific characters unlocks access to otherwise inaccessible areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/28c12acc73453f6aa3d8ca77de1b87cf.webp?t=1728683039\" width=614 height=45 /></span>This game aims to recapture the vibe of classic Collect-a-Thon games from the Nintendo 64 era, in a manner that energizes both exploration and the progression of the story. A unique object based smell mechanic will help the player find the different collectibles, some of which will allow him to build surprising context based structures. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/3e54aa6ddd868776571e8112ad48a08c.poster.avif?t=1728683039\" width=614 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/3e54aa6ddd868776571e8112ad48a08c.webm?t=1728683039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/3e54aa6ddd868776571e8112ad48a08c.mp4?t=1728683039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/9232ddba9c5944558351840df23a8114.webp?t=1728683039\" width=614 height=47 /></span>Numerous in-game abilities draw inspiration from real-life rat behaviors, gamified to provide action-oriented gameplay. The rat movements are crafted to be fluid, allowing a fast-paced and dynamic exploration of the world. You’ll also get to fight enemies and bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Nous remercions le Conseil des arts du Canada de son soutien.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>We acknowledge the support of the Canada Council for the Arts.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/a6d79b319a76aa22b901ded1aa2e9086.avif?t=1728683039\" width=500 height=92 /></span></p>",
